{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-posts-asciidoc-page-attributes-slug-tsx","path":"/posts/ubuntu-install-oh-my-zsh/","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"d791cff8-aa4a-521b-8037-1f21bdd0f91a","html":"<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_安装\"></a>安装</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>安装 zsh</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">sudo apt install zsh</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>将 zsh 设置为默认 shell</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">chsh -s $(which zsh)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>安装 <a href=\"https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh\">oh-my-zsh</a></strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">sh -c \"$(wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)\"</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_配置\"></a>配置</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>配置 zsh plugins</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>编辑 <code>~/.zshrc</code></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">plugins=(rails git ruby)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>agnoster 主题乱码</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">sudo apt-get install fonts-powerline</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>设置 <code>powerline</code> 字体即可</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>配置 <a href=\"https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/tree/master/plugins/emacs\">emacs</a> plugins</strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>e</code> 或 <code>emacs</code> 启动 emacs 客户端窗口，ssh 或容器终端会闪退</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>te</code> 启动 emacs 客户端终端模式</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"Ubuntu 安装配置 oh-my-zsh"},"pageAttributes":{"slug":"ubuntu-install-oh-my-zsh","category":"tool"},"revision":{"date":"2018-04-21","number":"1.0"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"d791cff8-aa4a-521b-8037-1f21bdd0f91a","pageAttributes__slug":"ubuntu-install-oh-my-zsh","__params":{"pageAttributes__slug":"ubuntu-install-oh-my-zsh"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3143286284"],"slicesMap":{}}